textAfterTable: Summary Within the 5 Gates of this project, Group 25 will disect and reassemble the Crafstman Eager-1 snow blower. This machine was built approximately in the mid to late 1970's and as such it is quite beat up and there is no product code to confirm its age. There are also a few minor pieces missing such as the air filter and the gas tank cap, which will not have an effect on the overall purpose of the assignment. The snow blower will be completely taken apart and analyzed on a piece by piece basis to obtain a better understanding of how the machine works over the following 5 gates: Gate 1 Product Predisection Analysis and Planning Gate1 Gate 2 Product Disection Gate2 Gate 3 Product Postdisection Analysis Gate 3 Gate 4 Product Explanation Gate 4 Gate 5 Product Delivery Gate 5 Retrieved from " http://gicl.cs.drexel.edu/index.php?title=Group_25_-_Snow_Blower_(Gasoline_Powered)&oldid=181139"
